c: 13
v: 2
t: "UMvelinqangi nguyena owaphakamisa amazulu ngaphandle kwezinsika ukuze nibone, wayesezibeka esihlalweni sobukhosi futhi wenza ilanga nenyanga ukuthi ngakunye kuhambe ngesikhathi esinqunyiwe, uhlela udaba (ngalunye) uwachaza ngobunjalo bawo amavesi ukuze niqiniseke ekuhlanganeni neNkosi yenu"